body.p:
If the font is available from a website (such as Google Fonts), simply select the font, along with its
      font weights and insert the generated @import declaration in your
      CSS:@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,300i,400,500,700i');

section h2 {
    font-family: Montserrat, Serif;
    font-weight:500;
}
